title: The Art Institute of Chicago On the Steps Magnet
description:
This magnet features a contemporary illustration of The Art Institute of Chicago’s entrance.

With thousands of possible journey combinations, the museum is never the same place twice. You, the visitor, make it come alive each day.

  • Dimensions: 2.5 x 3.5 inches.
  • Single Magnet.
  • Illustration by: Morgan Ramberg
